{"tid":1937563,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[認真]有冇巴打可以幫Android寫番套輸入法","createTime":"2020-03-22T04:20:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T03:26:05.000Z","uid":342282,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8fff566e57442188cb601ea50929e2a649c816f6","tid":1937563,"uid":342282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T04:20:31.000Z","msg":"5年前到宜家一直用緊simplified changjie keyboard<br />\n差唔多係我用過咁多輸入法入邊最強<br />\n中英輸入唔洗轉換 , 打字有時中英夾集可以仲快過用電腦打<br />\n又內置左港式用字&quot;系呢囉吓&quot;果d , 又有潮語係埋入邊 ( 當年既潮語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) &quot;有圖有真相, 你真識食&quot; 部分仲到宜家都有用<br />\n好可惜就係作者晨早好似已經放棄左更新...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 所以介面仲係好舊<br />\n同埋呢個輸入法無得用手寫, 同埋無得用emoji<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望有巴打可以幫android寫番套真係好用既輸入法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔介意課金"},{"pid":"e9e55eefa544113c99540466871b407264267c62","tid":1937563,"uid":342282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T04:24:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5b53da68ab06223f078eb7877a3bbb380600678","tid":1937563,"uid":156133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T04:52:12.000Z","msg":"我第一部手機係Android 2.2<br />\n當年有套輸入法叫CedIME, 好撚好用<br />\n不過後尾斷咗更新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家用Android焗住用Gboard<br />\n選字好唔撚柒方便, 冇得常用字前排<br />\n右冇得拖動選字, 次次都要撳粒下三角打開揀...<br />\n我都好想有新嘅輸入法出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ea2080f81563ee3566ddaaa52fa69c8b3da4388","tid":1937563,"uid":342282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5b53da68ab06223f078eb7877a3bbb380600678","tid":1937563,"uid":156133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T04:52:12.000Z","msg":"我第一部手機係Android 2.2<br />\n當年有套輸入法叫CedIME, 好撚好用<br />\n不過後尾斷咗更新<img src=\"/assets/f